<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <title>NiagaHoster | Welcome</title>
    
    <!-- Styles -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/assets/css/app.css">

    <!-- Scripts -->
    <script src="/assets/js/app.js"></script>
</head>

<body>

    {% include 'blocks/header.html.twig' %}

    <section class="border-b border-gray-200">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center">
                <div class="flex-auto xl:flex-1 max-w-lg py-16">
                    <div class="text-roboto-bold font-black text-4xl mb-8">PHP Hosting</div>
                    <div class="text-3xl mb-8">Cepat, handal, penuh dengan modul PHP yang Anda butuhkan</div>
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li>Solusi PHP untuk performa query yang lebih cepat.</li>
                        <li>Konsumsi memori yang lebih rendah.</li>
                        <li>Support PHP 5.3, PHP 5.4, PHP 5,5, PHP 5.6, PHP 7</li>
                        <li>Fitur enkripsi lonCube dan Zend Guard Loaders</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
                <div class="flex-1 min-w-full xl:min-w-0 flex justify-center xl:justify-end py-8">
                    <img class="max-w-xl" src="/assets/svg/illustration%20banner%20PHP%20hosting-01.svg" alt="PHP7" />
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    
    <section class="border-b border-gray-200">
        <div class="container mx-auto">
            <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-32">
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row flex-wrap justify-center items-center py-16">
                    <div class="flex-auto lg:flex-1 flex flex-col justify-end items-center mb-8">
                        <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-48 h-48">
                            <img class="w-48 h-auto" src="/assets/images/img-zendguard.jpg" alt="zendguard" />
                        </div>
                        <div>PHP Zend Guard Loader</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-auto lg:flex-1 flex flex-col justify-end items-center">
                        <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-48 h-48">
                            <img class="w-32 h-auto" src="/assets/images/img-composer.jpg" alt="composer" />
                        </div>
                        <div>PHP Composer</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-auto lg:flex-1 flex flex-col justify-end items-center">
                        <div class="flex justify-center items-center w-48 h-48">
                            <img class="w-48 h-auto" src="/assets/images/img-ioncube.jpg" alt="ioncube" />
                        </div>
                        <div>PHP ionCube Loader</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col justify-center items-center py-16">
                    <div class="text-roboto-bold font-black text-4xl">Paket Hosting Singapura yang Tepat</div>
                    <div class="text-3xl">Diskon 40% + Domain dan SSL Gratis untuk Anda</div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row justify-center items-start text-roboto">
                    {% for item in config.packages %}
                    <div class="relative text-center border rounded {{item.best_seller ? 'z-10 best-seller border-blue-500 border' : 'border-gray-200'}} mt-8">
                        <div class="text-roboto-bold font-black text-2xl p-2 border-t border-b {{item.best_seller ? 'bg-blue-500 text-white border-blue-500' : '' }}">{{ item.title }}</div>
                        <div class="text-montserrat p-2 border-b {{item.best_seller ? 'bg-blue-500 text-white border-blue-500' : '' }}">
                            <div class="line-through">Rp {{ item.price_original // 1000 }}.{{ item.price_original % 1000 }}</div>
                            <div class="flex items-start justify-center space-x-1"><span>Rp</span><span class="text-montserrat-black text-4xl font-black">{{ item.price // 1000 }}</span><span class="text-montserrat-black font-bold">.{{ item.price % 1000 }}</span>/ bln</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-2 border-b {{item.best_seller ? 'bg-blue-600 text-white border-blue-500' : '' }}"><span class="font-bold">{{ item.jumlah_pengguna | number_format(0,',','.') }}</span> Pengguna Terdaftar</div>
                        <div class="p-2 pt-8 border-b">
                            <p class="font-bold">{{ item.feature_title }}</p>
                            {% for feature in item.feature %}
                            <p class="leading-10">{{ feature | parse_feature_detail | raw }}</p>
                            {% endfor %}
                            <button class="{{item.best_seller ? 'button-blue' : 'button-black'}} mt-16 mb-8">{{ item.button }}</button>
                        </div>
                        {% if item.best_seller %}
                        <img class="absolute -top-2 -left-2" src="/assets/images/tag-best-seller.png" />
                        {% endif %}
                    </div>
                    {% endfor %}
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
                <div class="text-center text-3xl mb-16">Powerful dengan Limit PHP yang Lebih Besar</div>
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row flex-wrap justify-center items-center text-center text-roboto w-full">
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li class="p-2 pl-6 border border-gray-100"><span class="w-96">max execution time 300s</span></li>
                        <li class="p-2 pl-6 border border-gray-200 bg-blue-50"><span class="w-96">max execution time 300s</span></li>
                        <li class="p-2 pl-6 border border-gray-200"><span class="w-96">php memory limit 1024 MB</span></li>
                    </ul>
                    <div class="hidden xl:block w-8"></div>
                    <ul class="feature-list">
                        <li class="p-2 pl-6 border border-gray-200"><span class="w-96">post max size 128 MB</span></li>
                        <li class="p-2 pl-6 border border-gray-200 bg-blue-50"><span class="w-96">upload max filesize 128 MB</span></li>
                        <li class="p-2 pl-6 border border-gray-200"><span class="w-96">max input vars 2500</span></li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center h-16">
                    <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-gray-200"></div>
                </div>
                <div class="text-center text-3xl mb-16">Semua Paket Hosting Sudah Termasuk</div>
                <div class="flex flex-col lg:flex-row flex-wrap flex-between justify-center flex-wrap text-roboto">
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-6">
                            <img src="/assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_PHP%20Semua%20Versi.svg" title="php" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-roboto-bold text-xl">PHP Semua Versi</div>
                        <div>Pilih mulai dari versi PHP 5.3 s/d PHP 7.</div>
                        <div>Ubah sesuka Anda!</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden lg:block w-8"></div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-6">
                            <img src="/assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_My%20SQL.svg" title="mysql" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-roboto-bold text-xl">MySQL Versi 5.6</div>
                        <div>Nikmati MySQL versi terbaru, tercepat dan</div>
                        <div>kaya akan fitur</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden xl:block w-8"></div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-6">
                            <img src="/assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_CPanel.svg" title="cpanel" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-roboto-bold text-xl">Panel Hosting cPanel</div>
                        <div>Kelola website dengan panel canggih yang</div>
                        <div>familiar di hati Anda.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden lg:block w-8"></div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-6">
                            <img src="/assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_garansi%20uptime.svg" title="garansi uptime 99%" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-roboto-bold text-xl">Garansi Uptime 99.9%</div>
                        <div>Data center yang mendukung kelangsungan</div>
                        <div>website Anda 24/7.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden xl:block w-8"></div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-6">
                            <img src="/assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_InnoDB.svg" title="unlimited innodb" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-roboto-bold text-xl">Database InnoDB Unlimited</div>
                        <div>Jumlah dan ukuran database yang tumbuh</div>
                        <div>sesuai kebutuhan Anda.</div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="hidden lg:block w-8"></div>
                    <div class="flex flex-col items-center mb-16">
                        <div class="w-14 h-14 mb-6">
                            <img src="/assets/svg/icon%20PHP%20Hosting_My%20SQL%20remote.svg" title="wildcard remote mysql" />
                        </div>
                        <div class="text-roboto-bold text-xl">Wildcard Remote MySQL</div>
                        <div>Mendukung s/d 25 max_user_connections</div>
                        <div>dan 100 max_connections.</div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="flex justify-center items-center h-16">
                    <div class="h-1 w-16 bg-gray-200"></div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="flex flex-col">
                <div class="text-center text-3xl mb-8">Mendukung Penuh Framework Laravel</div>
                <div class="flex flex-wrap justify-center items-center">
                    <div class="flex-auto xl:flex-1 max-w-xl py-16">
                        <div class="flex flex-col">
                            <div class="mb-8">
                                Tak perlu menggunakan dedicated server ataupun VPS yang mahal. Layanan PHP hosting murah kami mendukung penuh framework favorit Anda
                            </div>
                            <ul class="feature-list text-roboto mb-8">
                                <li><span>Install Laravel <b>1 klik</b> dengan Softaculous Installer.</span></li>
                                <li><span>Mendukung ekstensi <b>PHP MCrypt, phar, mbstring, json,</b> dan <b>fileinfo.</b></span></li>
                                <li><span>Tersedia <b>Composer</b> dan <b>SSH</b> untuk menginstal packages pilihan Anda.</span></li>
                            </ul>
                            <div class=" text-xs mb-8">Nb. Composer dan SSH hanya tersedia pada paket Personal dan Bisnis</div>
                            <div>
                                <button class="button-blue">Pilih Hosting Anda</button>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex-1 min-w-full xl:min-w-0 flex justify-center xl:justify-end py-8">
                        <img class="max-w-xl" src="/assets/svg/illustration%20banner%20support%20laravel%20hosting.svg" alt="mbstring json phar" />
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

